wmnlibnotation.noteobjects

Class Measure

  • java.lang.Object
    • wmnlibnotation.noteobjects.Measure
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<Durational>

    public class Measure
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<Durational>
    Class that defines a measure. A measure may contain multiple voices that are referred to using voice numbers. This class is immutable. Use the MeasureBuilder class for easier creation of Measures.
    Author:
